com.facebook.widget

Class FacebookDialog.OpenGraphMessageDialogBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.widget.FacebookDialog.Builder<CONCRETE>
      • com.facebook.widget.FacebookDialog.OpenGraphMessageDialogBuilder
  • Enclosing class:
    FacebookDialog

    public static class FacebookDialog.OpenGraphMessageDialogBuilder
extends FacebookDialog.Builder<CONCRETE>
    Provides a builder which can construct a FacebookDialog instance suitable for presenting the native Open Graph action message dialog. This builder allows the caller to specify binary images for both the action and any Open Graph objects to be created prior to publishing the action. This builder will throw an exception if the Facebook application is not installed, so it should only be used if FacebookDialog.canPresentOpenGraphMessageDialog(android.content.Context, com.facebook.widget.FacebookDialog.OpenGraphMessageDialogFeature...) indicates the capability is available.
